      <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R17"/>
      <p><a href="ch70s03.html#MonstersO-R17">Oozes</a> are amorphous creatures that live only to eat. They inhabit underground areas throughout the world, scouring caverns, ruins, and dungeons in search of organic matter-living or dead.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2042770"/>Combat</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">monsterinfo</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R18"/>
        <p><a href="ch70s03.html#MonstersO-R17">Oozes</a> attack any creatures they encounter. They lash out with pseudopods or simply engulf opponents with their bodies, which secrete acids that help them catch or digest their prey.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2042802"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R19"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Blindsight (Ex):</strong></span> An <a href="ch70s03.html#MonstersO-R17">ooze's</a> entire body is a primitive sensory organ that can ascertain prey by scent and vibration within 60 feet.</p>
          <p/>
